y: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;'><span style="color:#ab1942;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">离开时还感叹：<br></span></span></section><section style='margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;'><span style="color:#ab1942;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">希望以后再来这里时</span></span></section><section style='margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;'><span style="color:#ab1942;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">阿富汗是另一个模样</span></span></section><section style='margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;'><span style="color:#ab1942;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">我再没机会回去过</span></span></section><section style='margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;'><span style="color:#ab1942;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">但20年过去了</span></span></section><section style='margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;li